data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms villa-style single family home in Dale City!  This beauty offers over 2400 sq ft of living space. The main floor includes 9ft ceilings, hardwood flooring on the entire level, remodeled powder room, spacious living and dining room area, bay window, eat in kitchen with newer appliances, recess lighting and plenty of windows allowing natural sunlight. The top level includes a primary suite with a walk-in closet, ensuite bath with soaking tub, separate showers and double vanities.  There are also two generous size bedrooms and a full bath located on this level. The fully finished basement includes a recreation area for entertainment, full bath, laundry room and bonus storage room. Last, but not least, the private backyard oasis is absolutely charming featuring a spacious deck with steps leading to the grassed fenced yard.  Perfect space for the family pet or entertainment!  This is an opportunity you don’t want to miss!  Book your showing today!
